{"tid":2050012,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗：若議員或參選人反對港區國安法　應被取消資格","createTime":"2020-06-04T00:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T01:33:09.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a5784eb5f65ddc05ce091d0656cc093a3b44c76d","tid":2050012,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1529994_1_20200603191304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1529994_1_20200603191304.jpg&h=0c0f566c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚耀宗認為，無論是議員或是參選人，都不應該反對為國家安全立法，否則是違反《基本法》，應被消資格。（紫荊網頁截圖）<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委譚耀宗說，國家安全法是每名港人應該遵守的法律，無論是議員或是參選人都不應該反對為國安法立法，否則是違反基本法，應被取消資格。<br />\n<br />\n有民主派議員批評譚耀宗的講法是製造寒蟬效應、唯恐天下不亂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529994-20200603.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529994-20200603.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraYwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=e75db11c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529994-20200603.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=58637d5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529994-20200603.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"16de8ff55013a25f8ac1cb6e2c6a6972c70b035f","tid":2050012,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:37:20.000Z","msg":"應該告顛覆國家政權<br />\n坐25年<br />\n終身剝奪政治權利"},{"pid":"8a081b0c191abee4cb6c1b466e085b1e9f4b40ce","tid":2050012,"uid":292267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"開始dq了"},{"pid":"6bb2d2d06e280dd5a35d24d6150b564db06954c5","tid":2050012,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"好大嘅官威呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}